PrecisAppointment of the following persons as directors of the board of directors of the Canada Pension Plan Investment Board, to hold office during good behaviour for a term effective March 22, 2001 and ending October 26, 2003. (HELEN K. SINCLAIR, of Toronto, Ontario, in the place of Susan Carnell, whose term has expired; GILBERT G. GILL, of Mount Pearl, Newfoundland, in the place of the Honourable Gérard V. La Forest, who has resigned; and MONIQUE LEROUX, of Outremont, Quebec, in the place of Pierre Michaud,
